          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audible Audio " href="/book/show/34234418-daemon">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/21276121-susan?shelf=audible">audible</a>, 
