          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3409532-april-does-feral-sometimes?shelf=omg-so-exciting-couldnt-stop-readin">omg-so-exciting-couldnt-stop-readin</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3409532-april-does-feral-sometimes?shelf=science-fiction">science-fiction</a>, 
