<span id="freeTextContainer8150211614754106620">I enjoyed this book and would recommend it to people who like technology thrillers or gaming. The plot was suspenseful and the technology was scary as hell. I have two minor complaints, though. First was the lack of depth in the characters; I didn&apos;t have any emotion or investment in what happened to them. Second was the ending. I&apos;ll just leave it at that since I don&apos;t want to give anything away.</span>
  <span id="freeText8150211614754106620" style="display:none">I enjoyed this book and would recommend it to people who like technology thrillers or gaming. The plot was suspenseful and the technology was scary as hell. I have two minor complaints, though. First was the lack of depth in the characters; I didn't have any emotion or investment in what happened to them. Second was the ending. I'll just leave it at that since I don't want to give anything away.</span>
